# Futrob core

Multi-tenant EA SPORTS FC competitions (MVP: FC Clubs) with hexagonal feature modules and Cloudflare Workers.

## Stack

- TanStack Start + React in `apps/web`
- Cloudflare Workers, D1, R2, Queues, Cron Triggers
- Better Auth (identity) + Futrob organizations (authorization)
- Hexagonal modules under `src/modules/*`; DI only in `src/di/`
- shadcn/Base UI, Tailwind, Vite+, Sentry at boundaries
- game-data providers: EA Clubs adapter today; manual/others later

## Vocabulary

Keep distinct: Encounter, OfficialMatchSlot, ProviderMatch, ExternalClub, OfficialMatchSelection, OfficialResult, Series (resolution), Standing, RankingSnapshot.

Do not use `EaMatch` / `ea-data` as domain names — use ProviderMatch / game-data (EA only in adapters).

## Non-negotiable

- scheduling ≠ game-data ≠ results ≠ statistics ≠ analytics
- Sync never auto-officializes
- `UNIQUE(provider_key, external_id)` for external refs
- Only approved official results update standings/rankings/public portal
- Organization-scoped D1 access; no Postgres RLS
- No Supabase/Vercel as Must platform

